WEBVTT

00:02.711 --> 00:07.172
<i>Anyone there?
I'm on channel four, like you said.</i>

00:09.426 --> 00:11.793
<i>I saw the video at a gas station.</i>

00:13.013 --> 00:14.629
<i>Name's Charles.</i>

00:14.723 --> 00:17.557
<i>Uh, people called me Chuck</i>

00:17.643 --> 00:20.010
<i>back when there were still people
to call me Chuck.</i>

00:21.522 --> 00:24.515
<i>When you get here,
I just want you to do one thing.</i>

00:26.026 --> 00:27.026
<i>Kill me.</i>

00:28.195 --> 00:30.006
<i>I got bit
while I was corralling some of the dead,</i>

00:30.030 --> 00:34.024
<i>and, well, I want to do what you said.
I... I want to help.</i>

00:35.202 --> 00:38.491
<i>The place I've been living, it's got
everything you need under one roof...</i>

00:38.580 --> 00:40.287
<i>uh, a book store,</i>

00:40.374 --> 00:42.741
<i>a bunch of places
to get clothes, a food court.</i>

00:43.293 --> 00:45.330
<i>Hell, there's even an Urgent Care.</i>

00:47.965 --> 00:48.965
<i>Are you there?</i>

00:50.551 --> 00:51.758
<i>Anybody listening?</i>

00:53.554 --> 00:56.388
<i>If you are, by the time you get here...</i>

00:59.142 --> 01:00.474
<i>I'll already be gone.</i>

01:01.895 --> 01:05.184
<i>I don't have a gun or I'd do it myself.</i>

01:05.274 --> 01:07.891
<i>Uh, I've got a red jacket on,
so I'll be easy to spot.</i>

01:08.735 --> 01:11.148
<i>Hell, I'll just hole myself up
in the security office.</i>

01:11.238 --> 01:13.070
<i>It'll make it easier for you.</i>

01:15.075 --> 01:19.911
<i>Find me. Bury me someplace outside.</i>

01:21.123 --> 01:22.123
<i>Just...</i>

01:23.625 --> 01:24.911
<i>put me under the stars.</i>

01:26.670 --> 01:27.831
<i>Yeah, that'd be nice.</i>

